Tecaching Assistance

CYB1003 - Introduction to Cybersecurity

Summer 2024

I've been offered to take charged of 2 groups of first year student in Computer Science, at the Université du Québec en Outaouais. Under the supervision of Myria Bouhaddi PhD, I was in charge of the lab sessions, where I was able to help the students with the following subjects :

  • Vigenere Cryptography
  • Substitution Cryptography
  • DES Cryptography
  • Public Key Cryptography
  • Hash Functions
  • Firewall
  • IDS
  • VPN
  • PKI
  • Security Protocols
  • Security Policies
  • Security Standards
  • Security Risks
  • Security Management
  • Security Audits
  • Security Incident Management
  • Security Incident Response
  • Security Incident Investigation
